Singer Akothee has warned her three daughters, Rue, Vesha and Fancy that she is not ready to be a grandmother. The singer had a talk with her children and demanded they introduce her to their boyfriends “I am paranoid because I don’t know who is dating my daughters,” she posted on Instagram “Let me enjoy myself, don’t give me the title grandma now. No babies in my house and 2020 introduce me to your boyfriends. That’s my motto by force or you go.” Rue her secondborn daughter replied, “Mum is focusing us to have boyfriends, but we don’t have boyfriends.”